{"tid":413514,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"係可口可樂做左pertime幾個月，你問我答","createTime":"2017-09-25T13:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T17:41:56.000Z","uid":148094,"like":6,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a978d065414070b15fcf8f16e146664b6f9902f","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:11:46.000Z","msg":"係可樂做左幾個月partime，基本上知大部分運作。有咩想問隨便問，識答一定用力答。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628254176cdb726975dd5d9fa0c4b3f341d5f3cd","tid":413514,"uid":30678,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:13:38.000Z","msg":"廿四味有邊廿四味?"},{"pid":"1e465b57d2d4915ade96e698af9c204416cc41e1","tid":413514,"uid":45494,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"可樂有咩咁可樂"},{"pid":"72d8a418ea4e6b149282df77e6b4e4b290155701","tid":413514,"uid":24981,"like":10,"dislike":13,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:15:28.000Z","msg":"點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2e86175d2924cbe9da57a4663d4080e85e6198","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:18:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廿四味有邊廿四味?</blockquote><br />\n唔知，因為你買到既健康工房廿四味唔係可樂廠做"},{"pid":"5ba68092222c7cb7d6a4b27a62326e54ee7f39d0","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可樂有咩咁可樂</blockquote><br />\n最可樂既地方係整果個位係好大陣臭糖味，但D人唔知照買"},{"pid":"6f7906553c903444dc5eed690be2a37ab0be44dd","tid":413514,"uid":37618,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:19:47.000Z","msg":"員工有咩着數"},{"pid":"7e749cd47aa4ee5b21458df31ee6ba0765aa66dd","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋"},{"pid":"6ba94564ee2b78c110e152e5997ab9928786db0d","tid":413514,"uid":43117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"有無見過蟲走黎走去"},{"pid":"c09c9369949e9058d1a91c83e3125de9395ededc","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>員工有咩着數</blockquote><br />\n最大既著數係廠證有得免費飲汽水，或者有時有D糖水食下咁。如果係特更或者夜更無份食糖水就送一張十蚊現金劵。"},{"pid":"1e2d7a6d46c41dd4c5b2aa6c734c64e8ef2d6a14","tid":413514,"uid":11793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n咁膠樽呢？"},{"pid":"4dfcc085d4de1b40f044c0eafbb8e0257d5f87e9","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無見過蟲走黎走去</blockquote><br />\n有，係生產線，倉同餐廳都見過好多甲由"},{"pid":"3eb9f8c72b36a9f36cbd3f9998681e0e8ea0116e","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":3,"dislike":28,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n咁膠樽呢？</blockquote><br />\n我霖同罐裝個問題都差唔多，不過因為個膠樽個口大D，你一次飲落去會感覺上比罐裝多氣D。"},{"pid":"ed0ff7d990d782ea1dad15586ece32fe3509d419","tid":413514,"uid":13978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:30:35.000Z","msg":"好無做？<br />\n學生想返三日請唔請？"},{"pid":"59fc05c1abdc61e6704dc7b2119ba43ccabc6a74","tid":413514,"uid":2373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:31:46.000Z","msg":"可樂迷留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0091f348600320f3a5a03c2baef79590b9fe56c","tid":413514,"uid":119389,"like":14,"dislike":25,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"做咩冇人屌pertime<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81fa87ce28b34367c83abf344bc8dae45b4b5ff","tid":413514,"uid":66494,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩冇人屌pertime<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92a3d79bbae43664f675c5149e764b30a0e7a97","tid":413514,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5cd1bbcd0de39bede749fb30884d4736df4dceb","tid":413514,"uid":68394,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:46:58.000Z","msg":"破解左條配方架未"},{"pid":"b6a61e328d0a5dcce0572bcb84b9f4f3ed1e313f","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好無做？<br />\n學生想返三日請唔請？</blockquote><br />\n睇下邊層樓同埋做咩位。有D位真係做到好眼訓，又有D位唔可以做錯，一做錯足以令到成條線唔洗開。因為我冇話一個固定位置，所以唔100%答你好唔好做，想知既你再詳細少少問。無得返三日，基本上返六日，有事請假都得不過要出聲。每日基本4個鐘。18歲以上先做得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082e6df8104ace27c82320a5c1814f1a4eb0c692","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"