"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌仲多過full time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2baf355bb6e45bd2fb7828f2421603d0ee7b1f","tid":413514,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"汽水任飲?"},{"pid":"36fcb66b931aa5119bee3e01f2378051d7103961","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好無做？<br />\n學生想返三日請唔請？</blockquote><br />\n睇下邊層樓同埋做咩位。有D位真係做到好眼訓，又有D位唔可以做錯，一做錯足以令到成條線唔洗開。因為我冇話一個固定位置，所以唔100%答你好唔好做，想知既你再詳細少少問。無得返三日，基本上返六日，有事請假都得不過要出聲。每日基本4個鐘。18歲以上先做得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n翻六日仲叫parttime <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌仲多過full time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npartime係個名尼嫁姐，咁佢是實上係比長工短鐘。"},{"pid":"b2c96978292d89a727aaeae9d8b0d4be13464527","tid":413514,"uid":2716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"人工幾多同有咩要做"},{"pid":"217074c2d71b40547f5fbb1fac355c2503394201","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":3,"dislike":73,"score":-70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>汽水任飲?</blockquote><br />\n理論上係。佢餐廳有兩部機可以禁，但係一個鐘只可以各禁一次。有時部機仲要神左就仆街。如果你系有做汽水既樓層到做野，有時大佬房會有汽水，不過唔係長期有，反而做水機水既樓層長期有膠樽雪碧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實夠薑唔怕比人屌既可以直接係線上面攞尼飲，係凍既。因為岩岩整出尼，所以我會叫佢做「新鮮可樂」。"},{"pid":"89c297937292f5873ffbe31cf51eecd0df6fb34f","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人工幾多同有咩要做</blockquote><br />\n60蚊粒鐘。如果無咩麻煩野搞，多數叫你埋機位幫手，話曬請你返尼係減輕長工壓力，會頂下食飯咁囉。工作上有少少搬野咁。如果有麻煩野或者其他樓層要求幫手，咁你就要上去幫手。叫得你走，你預自己又要搬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果唔好彩上倉，你搬果D野飲係幾排包埋做1 set，係好撚重，做到手都軟埋。"},{"pid":"534edf3d96eaba9a74fc6e7883cdb0ec94a8ec60","tid":413514,"uid":116045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:26:02.000Z","msg":"聰哥係咪仲做緊可樂"},{"pid":"e813dab3ba6c67a3907c32ca61a28d1da06e7bec","tid":413514,"uid":116045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:27:28.000Z","msg":"記得整可樂果層有飛哥白頭佬仲有歐陽"},{"pid":"6fd94832d16c9bebd5045d46091cd3e0101a9836","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得整可樂果層有飛哥白頭佬仲有歐陽</blockquote><br />\n有做可樂既至少都三層，唔知你所講既朋友係屬於邊層。"},{"pid":"79041b3be969df7ad4e3670bde78034ef2934fb1","tid":413514,"uid":116045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>記得整可樂果層有飛哥白頭佬仲有歐陽</blockquote><br />\n有做可樂既至少都三層，唔知你所講既朋友係屬於邊層。</blockquote><br />\n好似8樓，我講造可可樂原漿，果時造可樂得一層係溝一筒筒料加糖漿<br />\n上邊d名師傅黎"},{"pid":"930d03976a86534f1c84f54706ae2cee832397a1","tid":413514,"uid":95030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"點樣先可以參觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25464e46e48680804f90da276d040e6f7410e0bf","tid":413514,"uid":116045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>記得整可樂果層有飛哥白頭佬仲有歐陽</blockquote><br />\n有做可樂既至少都三層，唔知你所講既朋友係屬於邊層。</blockquote><br />\n好似8樓，我講造可樂原漿，果時造可樂得一層係溝一筒筒料加糖漿<br />\n上邊d名師傅黎</blockquote>"},{"pid":"bfcdd6ef6f6ed8c588efc7b1f9f20defdf9feacd","tid":413514,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:48:08.000Z","msg":"我係美國可口可樂股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1312b30cd79dff4c5759a7debadc17130b2af126","tid":413514,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"老豆係可樂老屎忽留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e846cebd1b6c2ee9545836c046cca5ec5fee87","tid":413514,"uid":57700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d6bb759880b502e9ea8810a9e33064ed4137079","tid":413514,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:00:22.000Z","msg":"幾時先出新配方嘅coke zero?"},{"pid":"a4e89973ec214c6ba424000e5177a4d1d38fa285","tid":413514,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玻璃樽裝d氣多到好爽<br />\n飲一大啖落去就gur到出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 實際上玻璃樽裝比罐裝多幾多氣知唔知<br />\n有無得量化"},{"pid":"404ee3a07135fa9b42a38e918e5c344651f2d53c","tid":413514,"uid":24981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玻璃樽裝d氣多到好爽<br />\n飲一大啖落去就gur到出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 實際上玻璃樽裝比罐裝多幾多氣知唔知<br />\n有無得量化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飲可樂冇氣真係唔飲 <br />\n點解人地個個國家都咁多氣<br />\n香港得個甜味"},{"pid":"22428f205552105f17ed97f34366880992cbb04c","tid":413514,"uid":101522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"個廠係咪石門個個？"},{"pid":"135a668d643284a0a9d4440cbfcd1cce045cd354","tid":413514,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玻璃樽裝d氣多到好爽<br />\n飲一大啖落去就gur到出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 實際上玻璃樽裝比罐裝多幾多氣知唔知<br />\n有無得量化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飲可樂冇氣真係唔飲 <br />\n點解人地個個國家都咁多氣<br />\n香港得個甜味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係要飲玻璃樽裝先夠氣<br />\n罐開完飲兩三啖之後就無晒氣<br />\n<br />\nbtw香港d可樂真係好平<br />\n外國可樂真係好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ee60ba607b9e3c9b0af39a6adcb0055cf27576","tid":413514,"uid":44301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:17:40.000Z","msg":"做左幾個月有冇肥到<br />\n見到咁既製造過程仲會唔會再飲或者少飲"},{"pid":"d27862d20e1e6bc1d7ed8f9adb6b6226af65d149","tid":413514,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"係咪有溶屍"},{"pid":"b60bd4f3f9c6bcff556c9be1c6e217daa393f175","tid":413514,"uid":84355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"點解可樂加冰底好飲咁多"},{"pid":"e7b5b87de484b31495f8efaa0f423257b787e6e0","tid":413514,"uid":7119,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:22:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾5p 做一世可樂仔啦"},{"pid":"381ee85249099d54897333b4bad88201ff9fdb68","tid":413514,"uid":32132,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:28:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 你尼撚完未 系撚完未？<br />\n負皮我俾嘅 返5p啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f58d0a188a61e2c0a65ae7e85d980a61160a5b","tid":413514,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>汽水任飲?</blockquote><br />\n理論上係。佢餐廳有兩部機可以禁，但係一個鐘只可以各禁一次。有時部機仲要神左就仆街。如果你系有做汽水既樓層到做野，有時大佬房會有汽水，不過唔係長期有，反而做水機水既樓層長期有膠樽雪碧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實夠薑唔怕比人屌既可以直接係線上面攞尼飲，係凍既。因為岩岩整出尼，所以我會叫佢做「新鮮可樂」。</blockquote><br />\n一定好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbbd35ab2f391fa71ed1c1290