9b","tid":413514,"uid":85210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n咁膠樽呢？</blockquote><br />\n我霖同罐裝個問題都差唔多，不過因為個膠樽個口大D，你一次飲落去會感覺上比罐裝多氣D。</blockquote><br />\n樓主你係做咩post? 如果係QC我諗你唔夠了解d產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申： 係可口可樂做左成年"},{"pid":"86611e4f97e379dfba811200abcd4854fccbc5d5","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玻璃樽裝d氣多到好爽<br />\n飲一大啖落去就gur到出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 實際上玻璃樽裝比罐裝多幾多氣知唔知<br />\n有無得量化</blockquote><br />\n可以試下用機器計下，或者我去查一查先。"},{"pid":"7f3bf1e3dc885e7605706382bbc9c5902f720e11","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玻璃樽裝d氣多到好爽<br />\n飲一大啖落去就gur到出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 實際上玻璃樽裝比罐裝多幾多氣知唔知<br />\n有無得量化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飲可樂冇氣真係唔飲 <br />\n點解人地個個國家都咁多氣<br />\n香港得個甜味</blockquote><br />\n我霖都關個罐事，因為香港個罐好薄+易穿。所以廢事比咁多co2你。不過我覺得日本可樂咁甜。"},{"pid":"0dc3dd6207c6e90ebb82a736266192fd2e90afff","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個廠係咪石門個個？</blockquote><br />\n石門對面小瀝源（近愉翠苑）"},{"pid":"8d001218315cbdd9ca6acb4ea0801c32c853f859","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玻璃樽裝d氣多到好爽<br />\n飲一大啖落去就gur到出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 實際上玻璃樽裝比罐裝多幾多氣知唔知<br />\n有無得量化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飲可樂冇氣真係唔飲 <br />\n點解人地個個國家都咁多氣<br />\n香港得個甜味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係要飲玻璃樽裝先夠氣<br />\n罐開完飲兩三啖之後就無晒氣<br />\n<br />\nbtw香港d可樂真係好平<br />\n外國可樂真係好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講無氣，7起先係王者，一打開飲第一啖已經無氣"},{"pid":"a8fb99a3b53b520e257cff272dd7779483df0643","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做左幾個月有冇肥到<br />\n見到咁既製造過程仲會唔會再飲或者少飲</blockquote><br />\n有肥到，個肚臍仔大左。但會照飲，只不過飲少D"},{"pid":"eadc160c192277a5eb5d72019727bfc2e6120d9a","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:34:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有溶屍</blockquote><br />\n唔係好明&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"ba9d411e96aa31f570615af811b0553a6c46afd5","tid":413514,"uid":37395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:34:41.000Z","msg":"試過飲左半罐，放左係office 半個鐘，飲到底有隻曱由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問過其他同事話未見過/聽過office 有曱由<br />\n<br />\n有無可能係罐入面本身有？"},{"pid":"eff94a39013c2d92fae4c48b122767faf8e5cccf","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解可樂加冰底好飲咁多</blockquote><br />\n又凍又多氣，係口腔刺激既高峰。"},{"pid":"a2fe6a0e3120e501f530fc2cceb97b672c392d21","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母 你尼撚完未 系撚完未？<br />\n負皮我俾嘅 返5p啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nok sorry sorry，打番系字。"},{"pid":"ccd9b0fe59b2fc59f5df23ac823c0d56a02d183b","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:40:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解麥當勞個d可樂好飲過超市買個d</blockquote><br />\nM記果D無咁濃味，溝co2多。所以會無咁甜，又覺得多D氣"},{"pid":"9e1a542274bee3e206186295c5aad31ac7c8b09e","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:41:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新個隻檸茶係咪足料</blockquote><br />\n果隻邊好飲&hellip;&hellip;唔通整果陣整D檸檬落去&hellip;&hellip;緊系化學野啦"},{"pid":"51fe85e1c2c2b29c043a4aad46ae9eb7328dddd3","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得zero sugar味道點，有冇可能代替到紅罐</blockquote><br />\n仲未試過，因為我飲到果D同原本無分別。"},{"pid":"8e9cd19e602afc8b660dc3dd598189c1556ed1fc","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:44:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解綠色果隻庶糖可樂香港廠房唔做<br />\n全部都係英國希臘入口，成$7-11罐</blockquote><br />\n應該系口味問題，同埋香港人無咁健康。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb04bbf073227304d522eb2d475b022cd1fa4ed","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有冇上18樓沖過涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沖涼未試過，因為住得過。但換衫果陣個個都露J。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17e9d5d088e8a944cd278a242b15abccecb15e8","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔再賣雲呢嗱可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該系味道問題"},{"pid":"ab5fc41462bfebed32e1ffa3b8e2f0f79d4415a9","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到底乾唔乾淨 日日都飲一罐 你講到生產線有甲由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為D汽水行緊果陣有機會撞到野撞穿（有時會發生）一穿就噴曬出去。咁搞到果D位有可樂流落地。咁倉一定有甲由啦，係倉攞D材料上生產線，結果D甲由就係果到生活啦。不過放心，整果個位係無可能有甲由。"},{"pid":"63b254d890b69dfa993dc41614cd6f16ab85d25b","tid":413514,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:52:38.000Z","msg":"系撚完未呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"e706c72cd1ad40a8ef9563903712aa4a4d245fa3","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主生產部果邊d員工伙記好撚團結<br />\n<br />\n千其咪撚做寫字樓果邊，d人事西撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂派系戰鬥爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nD hr請幾撚多人都哂時間</blockquote><br />\n60蚊一粒鐘都有派系鬥爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔係全部都parttime嘅我諗<br />\n何況有人就有是非架啦<br />\n做義工都有啦</blockquote><br />\n生產線都有閪人嫁，番緊工果陣因為你幫佢做野，所以就又乜又柒，又話努力向上。好啦，幫完放工就當你臭四，無視我依個人。<br />\nP.S.做人地樓層發生依件事"},{"pid":"beb42b074d7cc05fb7dabb5baef499f4f8b868a6","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時出返冰極雪碧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未聽過有重出依樣野既計劃，所以&hellip;&hellip;幫你唔到"},{"pid":"c5dc9b6c0cbaab5df57732fe3ab2d143f839b900","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n咁膠樽呢？</blockquote><br />\n我霖同罐裝個問題都差唔多，不過因為個膠樽個口大D，你一次飲落去會感覺上比罐裝多氣D。</blockquote><br />\n樓主你係做咩post? 如果係QC我諗你唔夠了解d產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申： 係可口可樂做左成年</blockquote><br />\n其實我做5+4號線，廢事講咁明比人炒"},{"pid":"37ebe252acf159e68f8ca773529fc273c0e94947","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過飲左半罐，放左係office 半個鐘，飲到底有隻曱由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問過其他同事話未見過/聽過office 有曱由<br />\n<br />\n有無可能係罐入面本身有？</blockquote><br />\n幾大隻先？"},{"pid":"6ec57dda74727e4347eac82d6735ec8f8c644df1","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>系撚完未呀屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n到底邊個正字&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我做左連登仔無耐炸&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d41c05d6955e7b318aaa2cf77e9c27320a555e4","tid":413514,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>系撚完未呀屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n到底邊個正字&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我做左連登仔無耐炸&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"25d83ace1707882890b16b90a1f3fe8d3dd4e0c7","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>系撚完未呀屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n到底邊個正字&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我做左連登仔無耐炸&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明明開post果陣打「係」&hellip;&hellip;打打下又比人屌5p&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"ab9159cde4654e5c400cc8f0f3cad74cb09d3cb4","tid":413514,"uid":73444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主生產部果邊d員工伙記好撚團結<br />\n<br />\n千其咪撚做寫字樓果邊，d人事西撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂派系戰鬥爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nD hr請幾撚多人都哂時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing 你以前做過可樂? <br />\n好了解內部文化喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3ad37790abf2c27382339d74050fc9f236cf98","tid":413514,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>系撚完未呀屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n到底邊個正字&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我做左連登仔無耐炸&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n關連登仔咩事<br />\n正常智商有讀過中學都唔會錯"},{"pid":"2f0de5faa2c3d5a28c1980f1f4805bdb2a0e7f64","tid":413514,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:28:04.000Z","msg":"見到最撚勁既工業意外係咩?"},{"pid":"8bc07d0cefaae2e00d3795a74dab82d4dda55a6e","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>系撚完未呀屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n到底邊個正字&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我做左連登仔無耐炸&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n關連登仔咩事<br />\n正常智商有讀過中學都唔會錯</blockquote><br />\n我本身打「係」字嫁&hellip;&hellip;可能係「尼」字出事&hellip;&hellip;咁「尼」既正字係咩？先謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94aa6027a8d87d1cb1ac9fa40b423ef8faa2ee1b","tid":413514,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"聽聞試過有人跌左落d可樂槽度熔左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1913ce1cb5c63e5e886e5c889fa793fa7462208b","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到最撚勁既工業意外係咩?</blockquote><br />\n最勁既工業意外係我，成日唔小心做野搞到有一排日日都見血。聽過個鏟車佬講有條友帶耳機渣鏟車，撞到人叫救命都唔知，攞7左十幾廿米先知仆街，比人撞果條友D骨移左位。"},{"pid":"f03fab5df95f00ce5108170947becdc130699914","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽聞試過有人跌左落d可樂槽度熔左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁撚大獲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c771e45b69ec1d3dd9f2f3f67b49cdbf5d5ff59","tid":413514,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:41:12.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇諗過進修中文?<br />\n平時有冇睇書?"},{"pid":"5e9c679253c7a605cc7ea6cb73d94207bbf38be1","tid":413514,"uid":116045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n咁膠樽呢？</blockquote><br />\n我霖同罐裝個問題都差唔多，不過因為個膠樽個口大D，你一次飲落去會感覺上比罐裝多氣D。</blockquote><br />\n樓主你係做咩post? 如果係QC我諗你唔夠了解d產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申： 係可口可樂做左成年</blockquote><br />\n4年前做，mary姐係咪仲做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f09c0410399271d32895ca8d9ffdcde33a42de4","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主有冇諗過進修中文?<br />\n平時有冇睇書?</blockquote><br />\n無睇書，等我即刻搵人補補鐘先"},{"pid":"fbcaabe6e81d095326cec2aab6ea2ec428cdd986","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解香港可樂咁難飲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難唔難飲好主觀，但係可以講既就係罐裝係無乜氣，好似飲糖漿咁，而玻璃既係太多氣，多到D可樂味都無埋</blockquote><br />\n咁膠樽呢？</blockquote><br />\n我霖同罐裝個問題都差唔多，不過因為個膠樽個口大D，你一次飲落去會感覺上比罐裝多氣D。</blockquote><br />\n樓主你係做咩post? 如果係QC我諗你唔夠了解d產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申： 係可口可樂做左成年</blockquote><br />\n4年前做，mary姐係咪仲做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係幾樓？做咩位？<br />\n#識唔曬咁多人#"},{"pid":"0c503a1e77020033ecff0cf202975d8121cb6ea8","tid":413514,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"