/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac974d98d7a1f0a262c15deb870d5ca6d478952f","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可樂廠有冇維他奶飲？</blockquote><br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cf59e3673a251cf1434e0f9bb11fb176e1e997","tid":413514,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可樂廠有冇維他奶飲？</blockquote><br />\n維他奶廠喺屯門㗎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdfa80739e68179644e2b5ba89f94b0fd9f7302","tid":413514,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:33:52.000Z","msg":"以前教我打乒乓球個呀sir都係可樂廠做，講緊都12、13年前，而家都應該退左休。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cc9932ff221c7a4097178299fb0ad89d089902","tid":413514,"uid":50097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:36:35.000Z","msg":"霖撚完未呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"252f190d007b8fd613c104457e9c5cfcfa62845d","tid":413514,"uid":148094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前教我打乒乓球個呀sir都係可樂廠做，講緊都12、13年前，而家都應該退左休。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有D長工同我講過，D人做左可樂基本上做到老，因為係唔洗技巧就做得，全部野都係形式化。但是實上依份正絕對唔好做，一更做十二個鐘，又熱。"},{"pid":"33d8475040f552a030f18bd7bd0a77200a9b7793","tid":413514,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>霖撚完未呀屌你老母<